' SD-06. UC-006 먼지 감지 이벤트 처리
' Related Use Case: UC-006. 먼지 감지 이벤트 처리
' Intent: 먼지 감지 시 증가 출력 수준과 유지 시간을 정책에서 조회하고 먼지 대응 상태를 시작하는 흐름을 표현한다.
' Note: 장애물 회피가 동시에 발생해도 증가 출력 상태는 유지한다.

@startuml SD_06_UC006_Handle_Dust_Detected
title SD-06 - UC-006 먼지 감지 이벤트 처리

actor "센서 입력" as Sensor
participant "RVC SW Controller" as Controller
participant "SensorState" as SensorState
participant "AutomaticCleaning" as Cleaning
participant "CleaningPolicy" as Policy
participant "DustResponse" as DustResponse
participant "CleaningCommand" as CleaningCommand
actor "청소 장치" as Cleaner
actor "Time" as Time

Sensor -> Controller: reportDustDetected()
activate Controller
Controller -> SensorState: update(dustDetected=true)
Controller -> Cleaning: handleDustDetected(SensorState)
activate Cleaning
Cleaning -> SensorState: isDustDetected()
SensorState --> Cleaning: true
Cleaning -> Cleaning: changeStatus(DUST_RESPONSE)
Cleaning -> Policy: increasedPowerLevel()
Policy --> Cleaning: INCREASED
Cleaning -> Policy: increasedPowerDuration()
Policy --> Cleaning: duration
Cleaning -> DustResponse: start(INCREASED, duration)
DustResponse --> Cleaning: active=true
Cleaning -> CleaningCommand: create(INCREASED)
CleaningCommand --> Cleaning: increasedPowerCommand
Cleaning -> Cleaner: setCleaningPower(INCREASED)
Cleaning -> Time: startTimer(duration)
Cleaning --> Controller: dustResponseStarted()

alt 먼지 대응 중 장애물 감지
    Sensor -> Controller: reportObstacleState(front=true)
    Controller -> SensorState: update(frontObstacleDetected=true)
    Controller -> Cleaning: handleObstacleWhileDustResponse(SensorState)
    Cleaning -> DustResponse: isActive()
    DustResponse --> Cleaning: true
    Cleaning -> Cleaner: keepCleaningPower(INCREASED)
    note right of Cleaning: 주행 상태는 UC-002 또는 UC-005를 따름
end

deactivate Cleaning
deactivate Controller
@enduml
